    "propId": "4a75b8df-3961-4bad-b142-6198b174ce99",
    "actorId": null,
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.interact",
        "name": "Interact"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "078c67f3-da48-4998-b3cc-af811836c9ca",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "a574d923-bddd-4eba-ab33-14eea1bca563",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0e3a9496-0923-40ae-abf9-9fb3b72554f3",
                            "text": "Look at the Suit of Armor",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d1b36fdf-c4c5-4fc2-9e47-e80c7be9d404",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "This armor used to belong to Sir Henry the Peckish. They say he died leading the Charge of the Light Brioche during the War of the Caterers, but that's just frippery.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "976b3fea-fac2-4ced-aea9-752291f13e56",
                            "text": "Read the Armor Instructions",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cbef882a-38c7-4fc6-9866-1dd34fb720be",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "There's a little plaque with instructions. It says, \"In case of invasion or other emergency, put on this armor before proceeding.\"",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5b3e51a2-ad43-46b3-9e3b-4c64ee41f9d6",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "That seems like good advice.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "ec28a31a-5eb6-4a19-ae0b-4475baba8ff6",
                            "text": "Wear the Suit of Armor",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7242fcbf-f6f0-43b1-b3b5-fffe6c7c6dd1",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "I'm not wearing that armor... it's haunted! They say that Sir Henry appears inside it every full moon, sneaks up behind people at the dinner table, and asks, \"Are you going to finish that?\"",
                                    "emotion": "3",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "7c71212c-f7a2-4db0-ad85-3c55213b8d86",
                            "text": "Take the Suit of Armor",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8af4e43b-07eb-4e46-9f92-8e45239acffe",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "But he makes such an appreciative receptacle for leftovers. Not that there ever are any.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "2",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "4fe7e42a-0e51-4537-980d-1add38f565b0",
                            "text": "Knock the Suit of Armor Over",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0b42e4c8-bfc1-4978-b836-7014b6ed465f",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "The occasional wine-soaked student has been known to topple one of these in the middle of the night and awaken the whole school. I don't want to be that student.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "5",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": true
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}